Package: inspectorORF
Title: An R package to plot Ribo-Seq and RNA-Seq coverage from ORFquant and RiboTaper outputs
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Eilidh", "Ward", email = "bs18e3w@leeds.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Isabel", "Birds", role = c("aut")))
Description: Utilises output from either ORFquant or RiboTaper, along with additional genomic or transcriptomic data, such as but not limited to RNA-Seq, long-read sequencing data, proteomics, Kozak scores etc to produce figures of transcripts or coding regions of interest with the ability to display multiple samples or conditions, codons of interest.
